From 90 to 93,
I've been more productive

50:10.216 --> 50:11.756
than I was when I was younger.

50:11.801 --> 50:14.801
I think I have, too,
because it's more fun.

50:14.846 --> 50:16.346
You wrote a book.

50:16.389 --> 50:18.009
Oh, I've written eight books.

50:18.057 --> 50:19.967
Eight books.
But in the last two years?

50:20.017 --> 50:22.727
Yeah, yeah, yeah. But it's fun,

50:22.770 --> 50:25.940
because you don't
have to do it, and if...

50:25.982 --> 50:30.692
