You're sunny lying
down, I'm sure.

51:09.609 --> 51:10.939
I mean, in bed, you're quiet.

51:10.985 --> 51:13.355
You smile. I know
you're a sunny person.

51:13.404 --> 51:17.664
Yes, I'm a sunny person
lying in bed with a smile.

