52:51.878 --> 52:53.708
Looking him right in the eye,

52:53.754 --> 52:56.464
I said, "You wished
to see me, Mr. Brynner?"

52:56.507 --> 52:59.087
He said, "Well, you know
I have to stay in my body."

52:59.135 --> 53:00.715
I said, "I understand."

53:00.761 --> 53:03.551
He said, "I just wanted
to welcome you to the show."

53:05.099 --> 53:07.559
Who was the person
who discovered the females?

53:07.602 --> 53:10.392
Bernie.

53:10.438 --> 53:13.188
<i>One morning, he got up smiling.</i>

53:15.484 --> 53:20.494
<i>So, he said, "I think
there's ladies here."</i>

53:20.531 --> 53:23.371
<i>So, I said, "What do
you mean?" You know.</i>

53:23.409 --> 53:26.119
<i>So, he said,
"'Cause in the night,</i>

53:26.162 --> 53:30.412
<i>I was thrilled
and delighted, see?"</i>

53:30.458 --> 53:33.038
<i>So, then he went
into such a story</i>

53:33.085 --> 53:38.335
that it's hundreds of years
later, I still blush.

53:38.382 --> 53:41.552
I love women, but I was
