53:44.513 --> 53:46.073
If they didn't ask me
to go to the prom,

53:46.098 --> 53:47.468
I didn't have a date.

53:49.518 --> 53:52.808
<i>But then I met someone
less than half my age...</i>

53:54.607 --> 53:57.517
