And so Dick gave me
this really nice brooch

55:31.078 --> 55:33.248
to kind of butter my mom up.

55:33.289 --> 55:36.249
<i>So, it was Thanksgiving,
and I... after dinner,</i>

55:36.292 --> 55:38.672
<i>I said, "Mom,
so I'm seeing someone."</i>

55:38.711 --> 55:40.961
And she... after, like,
the fifth guess,

55:41.005 --> 55:42.085
she finally said, "Dick?"

55:42.131 --> 55:44.511
I went, "Yes." "Oh."

55:44.550 --> 55:46.550
And I went,
"Here's this brooch."

55:51.057 --> 55:53.217
Dick: <i>We're friends first.</i>

55:53.267 --> 55:55.557
<i>You know,
the honeymoon is soon over.</i>

55:55.603 --> 56:00.403
<i>The notion of romance and that
kind of love fades pretty quickly,</i>

56:00.441 --> 56:02.781
but when you really care
about the other person...

56:02.818 --> 56:05.318
I'm her best friend,
and she's my best friend.

56:07.531 --> 56:11.331
I just feel like we are a new
model for a huge age difference.

56:11.368 --> 56:12.908
It can work.

56:12.953 --> 56:15.043
I mean, I don't think
just I could get along

56:15.081 --> 56:17.661
with just any 90-year-old
man this way.

56:17.708 --> 56:21.628
He's just a very special human
