56:24.548 --> 56:26.168
Love is the basis of everything,

56:26.217 --> 56:29.007
the key to all enjoyment
of living.

56:29.053 --> 56:31.143
Love... people think
of love as like,

56:31.180 --> 56:33.970
you know, marriage
and their family.

56:34.016 --> 56:36.346
You know,
that's very hard to find,

56:36.393 --> 56:39.563
perfect love, in all these
situations with humans,

56:39.605 --> 56:42.765
but you can find perfect love
in a lot of other places.

56:42.817 --> 56:45.317
Whether you're 9 or 90,

56:45.361 --> 56:49.071
do what you love,
but do it every day.

56:56.580 --> 56:59.000
Fields: <i>The more I play,
