57:40.624 --> 57:43.504
<i>like "Miami Beach Rumba."</i>

57:43.544 --> 57:46.214
<i>Then I wrote
"Managua Nicaragua"...</i>

57:49.008 --> 57:53.888
<i>which was on the Hit Parade
