People ask me
where I get my vitality,

01:03:43.445 --> 01:03:45.945
and to tell you the truth,
I haven't got a clue.

01:03:45.989 --> 01:03:47.819
I drag myself around.

01:03:47.866 --> 01:03:50.906
I push myself beyond endurance,
but that's how I am.

01:03:50.953 --> 01:03:53.333
<i>I guess the man upstairs
is helping me.</i>

01:03:55.415 --> 01:03:58.075
<i>For me, work is great fun.</i>

01:03:58.126 --> 01:04:00.746
I love what I do,
and it's much more interesting

01:04:00.796 --> 01:04:03.416
than sitting around
with a bunch of dopey dames.

